Class DecimalLiteral

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.rdf4j.model.impl.SimpleLiteral
      • org.eclipse.rdf4j.model.impl.DecimalLiteral
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Literal, Value

    public class DecimalLiteral
extends SimpleLiteral
    An extension of SimpleLiteral that stores an integer value using a BigDecimal object.
    Author:
    Arjohn Kampman
